Well Antiar, heres the problem. I'm addressing the big boys, not so much the babies as far as concerning Necro's. I don't know what you have been killing that can pump out Lv 60 in 18 less /played days w/o fear kiting, but hell back in the day... that would have some amazing shit. Maybe I'm living in the past and fear kiting is just obsolete now...fuck, can someone fill me in? Oh yea, forgot, twinking/PLing at its best. We got millions of Z-heart and then KEI buffs and all that other bullshit flowing around...fuck I'm stupid! Jesus, I'm living in the past. But yea, not everyone has the opportunity like you have of doing shit and fear kiting is one of the only viable ways to kill a mob.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Agro kiting is fixed now with the burst damage mini-patch, but I levelled 58-60 in those 3-4? days between the patch that supposedly broke agro kiting and the fix. All my xp'ing was agro-kite. I lost maybe 2 or 3 pets in that time I normally wouldn't have. It wasn't that bad. Maybe it would've been harder with a pet like 63 rogue, but with EoT at least it wasn't a prob. Either way its fixed now.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
