It's not they may have, they have nerfed it to shit. Wonder why shit doesn't really affect you? Because omg, Pre-POP mobs aren't buffed outta the ass with resists! You can still charm shit as far as Rev's in the Grey, or skel in ME or whatever because they didn't touch the spell one bit and works as it did before. The only difference is now that the spell now costs you up to 33% exp, but thats really nothing. My point is this, why give a fucking 65 rune word spell that does absolutely nothing but fill in an extra spell slot and oh my! Charm those darn blue sun rev's in Grey. Fuck, I'd rather have a gay spell like Illusion: Froglok than the charm now. At least I can show people my &quot;eliteness&quot; with that spell. But yea, your living in those golden level's like 1-10 where you have no care in the world till hitting 11 and shits starting to suck. When you get to where the rest of the Necro's are having trouble with, maybe I'll see you on here w/ your glorious rant post.<br>
